'''Gastón Hernán Olveira Echeverría''' (born 21 April 1993) is a professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]] for [[Paraguayan Primera División]] club [[Club Olimpia]]. Born in Uruguay, he plays for the [[Paraguay national football team|Paraguay national team]].

==Club career==
Olveira began his career in 2013 with [[Club Atlético River Plate (Montevideo)|River Plate Montevideo]]. He made his league debut for the club on 19 April 2014 in a 2–1 away defeat to [[Sud América]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2014/04/19/uruguay/primera-division/institucion-atletica-sud-america/ca-river-plate/1652966/|title=Sud America vs. River Plate – 19 April 2014 – Soccerway|website=int.soccerway.com|access-date=23 February 2019}}</ref>

On 17 January 2021, [[Club Olimpia]] announced the signing of Olveira on a season long loan deal.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://versus.lanacion.com.py/versus/2021/01/17/olimpia-presenta-a-su-nuevo-arquero-el-uruguayo-gaston-olveira/|title=Olimpia presenta a su nuevo arquero, el uruguayo Gastón Olveira|access-date=10 February 2021}}</ref> At the end of the year, River Plate bought Olveira from River Plate and signed him on a permanently 4-year deal.<ref>[https://versus.lanacion.com.py/versus/2021/12/31/river-plate-de-uruguay-oficializa-la-continuidad-de-gaston-olveira-en-olimpia/ River Plate of Uruguay formalizes the continuity of Gastón Olveira in Olimpia], versus.lanacion.com.py, 31 December 2021</ref>

==International career==
Olveira was part of Uruguay squad which won gold medal at the [[Football at the 2015 Pan American Games – Men's tournament|2015 Pan American Games]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Panamericanos: definidos los 18|url=https://www.futbol.com.uy/Deportes/Panamericanos-definidos-los-18-uc275949|access-date=12 October 2019}}</ref> On 11 October 2019, he received his first call-up to the [[Uruguay national football team|Uruguay national team]] as a replacement for [[Fernando Muslera]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Gastón Olveira convocado|url=https://www.auf.org.uy/gaston-olveira-convocado/|access-date=12 October 2019}}</ref> On 21 October 2022, he was named in Uruguay's 55-man preliminary squad for the [[2022 FIFA World Cup]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Selección: Diego Alonso entregó la lista de 55 reservados para el Mundial de Catar|url=https://www.futbol.com.uy/Deportes/Seleccion-Diego-Alonso-entrego-la-lista-de-55-reservados-para-el-Mundial-de-Catar-uc835965|date=21 October 2022|access-date=21 October 2022|language=es}}</ref>

He was naturalized as Paraguayan in 2026, and was called up to the [[Paraguay national football team|Paraguay national team]] in March 2026.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.elobservador.com.uy/futbol-internacional/tras-nacionalizarse-el-uruguayo-gaston-olveira-tendra-su-debut-el-arco-la-seleccion-paraguay-esta-fecha-fifa-n6038804|title=Tras nacionalizarse, el uruguayo Gastón Olveira tendrá su debut en el arco de la selección de Paraguay en esta Fecha FIFA|website=El Observador}}</ref>

